Rights.rightsHolderContact: UCLA Charles E. Young Research Library Department of Special Collections, A1713 Young Research Library, Box 951575, Los Angeles, CA 90095-1575. E-mail: spec-coll@library.ucla.edu. Phone: (310)825-4988
Title: Biographical files (UCLA University Archives Reference Collection). 1882-2012
AltTitle.other: University Archives Biographical files|~|UCLA University Archives. Biographical files (Reference Collection)
Description.note: Record Series 745 contains biographical information and photographs of faculty and staff affiliated with: the Los Angeles State Normal School (LASNS), 1881-1919; the University of California, Southern Branch, 1919-1926; the University of California, Los Angeles, 1927- . Materials include curriculum vitae, photographs, press releases, and newspaper clippings.
Summary: The UCLA University Archives reference collection of biographical files was created ca.1986 and contain information on: faculty and staff of the Los Angeles State Normal School (LASNS), 1881-1919; faculty and staff of the University of California, Southern Branch, 1919-1926; faculty and staff of the University of California, Los Angeles, 1927- .
